ActFirst Nations Fiscal and Statistical Management Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Schedule to the First Nations Fiscal and Statistical Management Act
PrecisOrder Amending the SCHEDULE TO THE FIRST NATIONS FISCAL AND STATISTICAL MANAGEMENT ACT by a) adding 2 First Nations in order to allow them to participate in the property tax regime established by the FIRST NATIONS FISCAL AND STATISTICAL MANAGEMENT ACT, and b) deleting one First Nation from the list, since it has become self-governing.
